"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jod1665702775423.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jod1665702775423.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jod1665702775423.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jod1665702775423\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Activate the worksheet plug-in form for the current main development\n    object.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104jod1665702775423_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"jod1665702775423__codeblock_g5t_mgm_mzb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation ws_activate \n params\n string pObjectUrl: IN\n endparams\n ; &lt;... Your code here ...&gt;\nend ; ws_activate</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jod1665702775423__section_xcb_4gm_mzb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d441492e54\">Parameters</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jod1665702775423__p_d4604e1_d4605e1_d4606e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword parmname\">pObjectUrl</span>—URL of the current main development object, in the format\n          <var class=\"keyword varname\">ObjectType</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">:</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ObjectName</var>. For example, <code class=\"ph codeph\">cpt:MY_COMPONENT</code>,\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">ent:SALES_ORDER.SALES</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">aps:MY_APP</code>,\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">libsnp:MYSNIPPETS</code>, and so on.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jod1665702775423__section_kgn_4gm_mzb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d441492e88\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jod1665702775423__p_d4613e1_d4614e1_d4615e1\">The <span class=\"keyword apiname\">ws_activate</span> operation of a worksheet\n        plug-in must have an IN string parameter to hold the value of the current object.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jod1665702775423__p_d4616e1_d4617e1_d4618e1\">It should contain <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">edit/nonmodal</span> command\n        to ensure the contents of the form are displayed.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jod1665702775423__p_d4619e1_d4620e1_d4621e1\">After it is executed, the <span class=\"keyword apiname\">ws_getsVisible</span>\n        operation of the plug-in Form is called.</p>\n</section>\n<div class=\"example\" id=\"jod1665702775423__example_cgm_sgm_mzb\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104jod1665702775423_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"jod1665702775423__codeblock_omr_sgm_mzb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation ws_activate\n params\n string pObjectUrl : IN\n endparams\n activate \"IDE_API_1\".outputMessage(\"Execute trigger (Url=%%pObjectUrl).\")\n if ($procerror != 0)\n putmess \"Activate error: %%$procerror%%%, %%$procerrorcontext%%%\"\n endif\n $URL$ = pObjectUrl\n URL.ENT = $URL$\n edit/nonmodal\n \nend ; operation ws_activate</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gwk1665702595783.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>edit</a><p>Display the component in preparation for user input.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528969\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528969\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ws_activate Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Nov 19, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Activate the worksheet plug-in form for the current main development object. Explain this code operation ws_activate params string pObjectUrl: IN endparams ; <... Your code here ...> end ; ws_activate Copy Parameters pObjectUrl —URL of the current main development object, in the format ObjectType : ObjectName . For example, cpt:MY_COMPONENT , ent:SALES_ORDER.SALES , aps:MY_APP , libsnp:MYSNIPPETS , and so on. Description The ws_activate operation of a worksheet plug-in must have an IN string parameter to hold the value of the current object. It should contain edit/nonmodal command to ensure the contents of the form are displayed. After it is executed, the ws_getsVisible operation of the plug-in Form is called. Explain this code operation ws_activate params string pObjectUrl : IN endparams activate \"IDE_API_1\".outputMessage(\"Execute trigger (Url=%%pObjectUrl).\") if ($procerror != 0) putmess \"Activate error: %%$procerror%%%, %%$procerrorcontext%%%\" endif $URL$ = pObjectUrl URL.ENT = $URL$ edit/nonmodal end ; operation ws_activate Copy Related Links edit Display the component in preparation for user input. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}